title: Frederic Remington and the Spanish-American War (Art Ebook)
description:
Crown | 1971 | Pdf | Eng | 178 pag | 31.7 MB

Over 100 illustrations

Even the most eager collectors of Frederic Remington's art are likely to know little of his reportage on the Spanish-American War. Although Remington's fame now rests with his Western art, he was very active in the 1890s as an artist-correspondent,  and one of his major assignments was the Spanish-American War
